flowchart TD
  RAW[Private source archive] --> INV[Hash inventory]
  RAW --> COMP[Version comparison]
  RAW --> PHOTO[Photographic inspection]
  INV --> REG[Source/conflict register]
  COMP --> REG
  PHOTO --> REG
  REG --> DOC[Public technical documentation]
  REG --> CODE[MATLAB / clean-room examples]
  DOC --> MATRIX[Evidence and verification matrix]
  CODE --> MATRIX
  MATRIX --> CV[CV wording]
  RAW -. excluded .-> MANIFEST[Excluded-files manifest]
